# Ignore everything by default.
*

# Allow Git to traverse directories.
!*/

# Track only these workspace directories and their contents.
!.agents/
!.agents/**
!.codebuddy/
!.codebuddy/**
!.claude/
!.claude/**
!AGENTS.md

# 但排除机器本地的权限/设置文件（每台电脑不同，不该同步）
.claude/settings.local.json

# Ignore local OS and Python cache artifacts.
**/.DS_Store
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc

# Keep this ignore file tracked.
!.gitignore
